    "body": "Delegation is opt in by design, because delegation adds overhead to token transfers (the checkpoint bookkeeping). If a token holder only wants to trade the token on a DEX, they are much better off without setting up a delegate.\r\n\r\nIn your code you can add `delegate(...)` right after `_mint` if you want to make it auto-delegate.",
